ZH: 这座小岛属于我们的国土。
EN: This small island belongs to our national territory.

ZH: 我们要保护祖国的国土。
EN: We must protect the national territory of our country.

ZH: 因为战争，许多国土遭受了破坏。
EN: Many territories were damaged due to the war.

ZH: 他们不断地扩大自己的国土。
EN: They are constantly expanding their territory.

ZH: 保护国土是每个公民的责任。
EN: Protecting the national territory is the duty of every citizen.

ZH: 这些岛屿是我们的领土一部分。
EN: These islands are part of our national territory.

ZH: 地图上标示着国土的边界线。
EN: The borders of the national territory are marked on the map.

ZH: 这个国家的国土面积非常广阔。
EN: The territory of this country is very vast.

ZH: 他们对国土的保护非常重视。
EN: They attach great importance to the protection of their territory.

ZH: 他们为了保卫国土，不惜付出生命。
EN: They are willing to sacrifice their lives to defend the national territory.

ZH: 国土的完整性是我们的底线。
EN: The integrity of the national territory is our bottom line.

ZH: 他们试图通过战争扩张自己的国土。
EN: They try to expand their territory through war.

ZH: 维护国土的安全是国家的首要任务。
EN: Ensuring the security of the national territory is the primary task of the country.

ZH: 我们将坚决保卫国土的领土。
EN: We will resolutely defend the territory of our national territory.

ZH: 国土的发展不应以牺牲环境为代价。
EN: The development of the national territory should not come at the expense of the environment.

ZH: 他们用围墙围住了整个国土。
EN: They surrounded the entire territory with a wall.

ZH: 那片红色的土地是国土的标志。
EN: The red earth is the symbol of the national territory.

ZH: 划定国土边界是国际法的一部分。
EN: Delineating national territory boundaries is part of international law.

ZH: 和平时期，国土安全是最重要的。
EN: In peacetime, national security is the most important.

ZH: 他们不断探索新的科技来保护国土。
EN: They are constantly exploring new technologies to protect the national territory.
